      <title>标准普尔 500 指数令人毛骨悚然的平静表明历史性反弹具有持久力量</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-03/eerie-calm-in-s-p-500-signals-historic-rally-has-staying-power</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在 11 月份股市飙升的肾上腺素激增的背后，是一种令人毛骨悚然的平静，这预示着股票投资者将获得更多收益，至少到今年年底是这样。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-03/eerie-calm-in-s-p-500-signals-historic-rally-has-staying-power</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 03 Dec 2023 15:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
